V0202_01_00_00_0.text: Heavy is the King's crown  - that's why only I can wear it!

V0202_01_00_01_0.text: I'll show you that my soul still blazes!

V0202_01_00_02_0.text: Remove your training wheels if you want to keep up with me!

V0202_01_00_02_1.text: Or I'll send you in for a permanent pit stop!

V0202_01_00_03_0.text: If you have the guts to face me, you have the guts to lose!

V0202_01_00_04_0.text:
Yusei!
I'll put my very soul into this Duel!

V0202_01_00_04_1.text:
So no one will pose a challenge!
Not even you!

V0202_01_00_05_0.text: We've achieved all we can as a team.

V0202_01_00_05_1.text: So I'll tackle new challenges solo from now on!

V0202_01_00_06_1.text:
...Very well.
I'll grant you a moment of the King's time.

V0202_01_00_07_0.text:
Carly...
Even if it costs me everything, I will save you!

V0202_01_00_09_0.text: The Mark of the Dragon yearns to Duel a Dark Signer.

V0202_01_00_09_1.text: And I shall grant its wish!

V0202_03_00_00_0.text: There's nothing left you can do!

V0202_03_00_01_0.text: The finish line is within sight!

V0202_03_00_02_0.text: Don't expect me to slow down!

V0202_03_00_04_0.text: Victory is to be taken, not given!

V0202_03_00_05_0.text: Humph! Your moves are nothing special!

V0202_05_00_00_0.text: Feast your eyes on King Jack Atlas's true power!

V0202_06_01_01_0.text: You best try harder than that!

V0202_07_09_01_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

I activate my Trap!

Red Nova Dragon!
Activate your effect!

V0202_09_00_08_0.text: Majestic Red Dragon's effect absorbs your monster's ATK!

V0202_09_00_14_0.text: I activate Barrier Resonator's effect from my hand!

V0202_09_00_17_0.text: Medium Piece Golem Special Summons a monster from my deck!

V0202_09_00_19_1.text: I Special Summon it from my hand!

V0202_09_00_20_0.text: I send Red Gardna from my hand to the Graveyard!

V0202_09_00_20_1.text: Now your effects can't destroy my monsters this turn!

V0202_09_00_21_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 3 or lower Fiend-Type Tuner!

V0202_09_00_22_0.text: Scarlight Red Dragon Archfiend's effect activates!

V0202_09_00_23_0.text: Tyrant Red Dragon Archfiend's effect activates!

V0202_09_00_24_0.text: Tyrant Red Dragon Archfiend's effect activates!

V0202_09_00_26_0.text: Red Dragon Archfiend/Assault Mode! Resurrect my monster!

V0202_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0202_37_00_00_0.text: As the King roars, feel the crushing blow of victory!

V0202_37_00_01_0.text: This red blade announces the King's verdict!

V0202_37_00_01_1.text: Surge with the flames as I Synchro Summon!

V0202_37_00_02_0.text: Behold as the stars high above in the sky...

V0202_37_00_02_1.text: And the fire deep down below in the earth...

V0202_37_00_02_2.text: Collide in a cosmic explosion to Synchro Summon!

V0202_37_00_03_0.text: With the wings of wind, I Synchro Summon!

V0202_37_00_04_0.text: This light shines upon the land as its true conqueror!

V0202_13_00_08_0.text: I give you Majestic Red Dragon!

V0202_37_00_05_0.text: The new sovereign emerges from the chaos!

V0202_13_00_20_0.text: Combine and form Multiple Piece Golem!

V0202_37_00_06_0.text: From the ancient chasms of a lost world...

V0202_37_00_06_1.text:
I awake a great and terrible power!
Synchro Summon!

V0202_13_00_26_0.text: Rise, my Scarlight Red Dragon Archfiend!

V0202_37_00_07_1.text: I call forth an absolute power destined to rule this Duel!

V0202_13_00_27_0.text: Bow down in terror before Tyrant Red Dragon Archfiend!

V0202_13_00_28_0.text: The conqueror emerges, clad in scorching armor!

V0202_13_00_28_1.text: Appear before me, Red Dragon Archfiend/Assault Mode!

V0202_37_00_08_0.text: Witness why I am known as the true King!

V0202_37_00_09_0.text: My crimson dragon shines upon the infernal path!

V0202_37_00_11_0.text: The king of the dark abyss unleashes its rage!

V0202_37_00_12_0.text: Mountains will crumble as the land is engulfed in flames!

V0202_37_00_13_0.text: Scorch the earth and stand at the apex of existence!

V0202_37_00_13_1.text:
Rule over all of creation!
Synchro Summon!

V0202_37_00_14_1.text: The ultimate destroyer arrives to bring your demise!

V0202_13_00_38_0.text: Hot Red Dragon Archfiend King Calamity!

V0202_13_00_39_0.text: Come forth, Gash the Dust Lord!

V0202_13_00_41_0.text:
The Tuner Monster arrives!
Majestic Dragon!

V0202_13_00_42_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Phantom King Hydride!

V0202_13_00_43_0.text: Here comes Absolute King Back Jack!

V0202_37_00_15_0.text: The star of doom comes to judge all living things!

V0202_37_00_16_0.text: The lone wolf with blue eyes incinerates the heavens!

V0202_37_00_16_1.text:
Show these lapdogs who bears the fangs!
Synchro Summon!

V0202_16_00_01_0.text: Feel the roar of the mighty!

V0202_19_00_06_0.text:
Stardust Dragon!
I command you to attack!

V0202_19_00_35_0.text: Attack, Hot Red Dragon Archfiend Abyss!

V0202_19_00_36_0.text: Attack, Hot Red Dragon Archfiend Bane!

V0202_19_00_38_0.text: Hot Red Dragon Archfiend King Calamity, break their spirit!

V0202_19_00_45_0.text: Celestial Wolf Lord, Blue Sirius attacks!

V0202_21_00_00_1.text: There's no escape route for you, except giving up!

V0202_21_00_02_0.text: You dare leave me in the dust?

V0202_28_00_00_0.text: There's only one Master of Faster! And that's me!

V0202_28_00_01_0.text: You've had your fun, but it's time for my victory lap!

V0202_28_00_02_0.text: With every Duel, my techniques are getting more powerful!

V0202_28_00_02_1.text: And one step closer to a perfect Duel!

V0202_28_00_03_0.text:
I'll Duel until my fire is extinguished!
Which is never!

V0202_28_00_04_0.text:
Yusei!
Only I rule the Duel!
As the one true King!

V0202_28_00_05_0.text: I want to test my skills on the world stage!

V0202_28_00_05_1.text:
And I'll defeat anyone who stands in my way!
Even Team 5D's!

V0202_28_00_06_0.text: Tell your editor to leave the front page open!

V0202_28_00_06_1.text: For a full-page spread on the Master of Faster, Jack Atlas!

V0202_28_00_08_0.text: You're a mere speed bump on my way to my true opponent!

V0202_28_00_09_0.text: Earthbound Immortals are nothing against the true King!

V0202_29_00_00_0.text: This defeat isn't enough to break my Dueling spirit!

V0202_29_00_01_0.text:
Humph!
I won't lose next time!

V0202_29_00_01_1.text: I know what true power is, and I'll use it to crush you!

V0202_29_00_02_0.text: There never was a King... until I showed up!

V0202_29_00_02_1.text:
So don't follow in my footsteps!
Create your own path!

V0202_29_00_03_0.text: I won't give up on my power Dueling style!

V0202_29_00_03_1.text: It's the only way I know how to fight!

V0202_29_00_04_0.text: So this is the bond you have with your monsters...

V0202_29_00_04_1.text: You've woken something new inside me, Yusei!

V0202_29_00_05_0.text: Seems you've given me a reason to come back here.

V0202_29_00_06_0.text:
Argh... Leo!
Don't you dare think you're better than me!

V0202_29_00_06_1.text:
Not even for a moment!
Got it?

V0202_29_00_07_0.text: You say that as the King, I must now treat you as my queen?

V0202_29_00_07_1.text:
......No, I can't do that!
Stop trying to trick me!

V0202_29_00_08_0.text:
No... This can't be...
From the depths of my heart...

V0202_29_00_08_1.text: I'll find a way to save you yet...

V0202_29_00_09_0.text: This won't go unforgiven, Dark Signer!

V0202_30_00_00_0.text: There's only one King! And you're looking at him!

V0202_30_00_02_0.text: The King never lets an opportunity pass!

V0202_33_00_00_0.text: Feel the fury of my soul!

V0202_33_00_01_0.text: There's only one way to Duel... and it's with power!

V0202_34_00_00_0.text: Only a fool doesn't comprehend my greatness.

V0202_34_00_01_0.text: I escape every scrape to energize the crowd!

V0202_34_00_02_0.text: I feel my soul raging with power!

V0202_34_00_03_0.text: Never forget that the King is always three steps ahead!

V0202_34_00_04_0.text: Can you keep up with the Master of Faster?

V0202_34_00_06_0.text: The King's Duel must always entertain!

V0202_34_00_08_0.text: Duel with your own style instead of copying others!

V0202_35_00_01_0.text: This Duel's about to hit the fast lane with Jack Atlas!

V0202_36_00_00_0.text: Let them know that this Duel is over!

V0202_36_00_02_0.text: I leave my fate to you!

V0202_36_00_05_0.text: Yusei... I leave the rest... to you...

V0202_36_00_06_0.text:
Go!
Show 'em the strength of Team 5D's!

V0202_36_00_07_0.text:
Get gritty!
Remember - we fight together!

V0202_36_00_08_0.text:
Don't give up!
I believe in you!
